1.5
log
@Same session_socket_blockmode() changes as done to ospfd. Also do the same
kroute change (make socket non-blocking and add trigger for partial reads).
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: control.h,v 1.4 2013/03/22 14:25:31 sthen Exp $ */

/*
